28-10-2020 
The biggest day of my life ❤️
.
Vo kehte h na kisi cheez ko itni shiddat se chaho toh puri kainat use pura karnee me judd jaati hai ❤️😀 toh bus esa hi kuch mere saath hua ❤️
I thank God for everything ❤️
It was my father's dream as he always wanted to see me on the NATIONAL TELEVISION 
So here I am doing what he always dreamt of ❤️ and what family dreamt of . 
And What I was dreaming since childhood 🤭
This is just a start and there is alot more 😀
Way to gooooo ❤️
I can't even explain this feeling in words but I can only say thanks to god🙏
 thanks to my family and friends for always being supportive ❤️
.
.
IMISSYOU PAPA ❤️ i know you r very proud 💗 just keep blessings me where ever you r right now
ILOVEYOU ❤️
.
